description: Try our easy to follow Wholemeal Scone Scrolls recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Wholemeal Scone Scrolls Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Arrange on baking paper lined oven trays, cut side down and bake for 15 minutes. Scatter with cheddar and bake for a further 10 minutes.
